 JOE JOHNSON: It's a wonderful feeling, and it makes you feel like all the work you've put it is really paying off.  
  
  Q. (Inaudible).   
 JOE JOHNSON: I think more than anything just all the guys being together and pretty much having camaraderie. It's fun for me. I enjoy playing with all these guys.   
   
